<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4720112>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figures 1–7. Stegana (Stegana) zhangi Sidorenko from Hainan, China, 1–5, male; 6, 7, female: 1, epandrium (epand), surstylus (sur), and cercus (cerc) (lateral view); 2, sur (frontal view); 3, hypandrium (hypd) and gonopods (gon) (ventral view); 4, parameres (pm), aedeagus (aed), and aedeagal apodeme (aed a) (ventral view); 5, hypd, gon, pm, aed, and aed a (lateral view); 6, epiproct (epi) and cerc (dorsal view); 7. oviscapt (ovi) (viz. sternite VIII) and hypoproct (hypo) (ventral view). Scale bars = 0.1 mm." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4720112/files/figure.png" .

